                            <comment id="14653089" author="ankurd" created="Tue, 4 Aug 2015 05:33:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Regression due to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/commit/a5ef58113667ff73562ce6db381cff96a0b354b0#diff-dded6985c865d7623d83ec5a860e1bd4R75&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/commit/a5ef58113667ff73562ce6db381cff96a0b354b0#diff-dded6985c865d7623d83ec5a860e1bd4R75&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
